            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "New record of the Wroughton’s Free-tailed Bat (Otomops wroughtoni) and its activity in the vicinity of wind turbines in western India",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Sreejith",
